{"tid":1376342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[極重要]如果你屋企附近放過催淚彈嘅一定要入黎","createTime":"2019-07-28T10:00:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T12:10:48.000Z","uid":264639,"like":280,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"90b0d5e24b0a538983922ac96e888c363c15ffa6","tid":1376342,"uid":264639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:00:15.000Z","msg":"有鑑於香港警察最近721同727都已經再無理到老人院，民居，高樓漏斗效應等到處亂丟催淚彈，唔係出去抗爭都分分鐘係屋企中招，老人家小朋友都一樣受到波及。所以本著自己香港自己救既心，上網做左少少research 綜合左幾篇CS(催淚氣) decontamination (去毒)的文章，想提供幾個可以徹底清除呢啲化學物質嘅方法，同注意的地方。唔正確請指點。<br />\n<br />\n屋企/老人院/村屋係元朗/中上環，當時打開左窗/有半露天/露天的地方尤其注意:<br />\n-窗簾，窗邊的家具，掛係出面既衣服等可以清洗的，通通盡快拆出拎去洗衣機洗走催淚的殘留化學物質<br />\n-曝露左係催淚下既食物，例如放左係枱既水果等等，請掉曬佢地，如果唔係有機會洗唔走食落肚<br />\n用大量水，或酒精base的清潔劑去抹下個窗/窗台/甚至窗出面<br />\n-如果真係好嚴重咁成個床褥，地氈都曝露左係催淚煙入面，可以考慮掉左佢地，因為有可能會好似二手煙咁既原理仲有殘留物質，咁就日吸夜吸二手催淚。<br />\n<br />\n如果關曬窗開左冷氣以為冇死，你又錯了。<br />\n有可能已經扯左d催淚入去通風系統/冷氣入面，一日唔搞一日你個冷氣吹出黎既都有可能有殘留化學物質。人地美國有專門的公司搞去毒，係香港點搞我真係唔知。有冇朋友可以俾d資訊係咪可以叫返我地個垃圾政府搞，定直接有事告佢拎返賠償(民事訴訟？)<br />\n<br />\n資料來源:<br />\n<a href=\"https://link.medium.com/UH3yNHCtGY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Flink.medium.com%2FUH3yNHCtGY&d=9l2h7zKZEd5x%2FdYTAZY3whZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=23fd847f\" target=\"_blank\">https://link.medium.com/UH3yNHCtGY</a><br />\nTear Gas Cleanup, Removal &amp; Neutralization Procedure<br />\nBy Restoration Pro Selection &bull; 18 May 2018<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.aftermath.com/services/specialty-services/tear-gas-cleanup\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aftermath.com%2Fservices%2Fspecialty-services%2Ftear-gas-cleanup&d=9l2h7zKZEd5x%2FdYTAZY3whZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=aede3eb1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.aftermath.com/services/specialty-services/tear-gas-cleanup</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/ershdb/emergencyresponsecard_29750033.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fniosh%2Fershdb%2Femergencyresponsecard_29750033.html&d=9l2h7zKZEd5x%2FdYTAZY3whZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=2ada0151\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cdc.gov/niosh/ershdb/emergencyresponsecard_29750033.html</a>"},{"pid":"36d5a4994315f6fdcc1df62acc96430cdb3fd582","tid":1376342,"uid":132083,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:01:21.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要比埋銀髮族睇！！"},{"pid":"012b35b4fbc6c786a8338c55af1bff0bd3ce18bf","tid":1376342,"uid":264639,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:02:01.000Z","msg":"幫手推俾d屋企人/老人家睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b89f2d749eaba2ff0cb7fb31b5f366d61df462d8","tid":1376342,"uid":264639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:02:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3ed2b5f659386f41b06bf7eb4d4a8e82dd375c1","tid":1376342,"uid":81693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:03:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f62a06c2ee6865fa37b6fc039fb13679676b68c4","tid":1376342,"uid":272573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:04:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"10b743ccd37582547ebe4706e8857130a613d280","tid":1376342,"uid":190962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:04:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62971c4af66ab1de4b8c5c69211b85aaa1110d43","tid":1376342,"uid":134054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:05:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb770246e54bb92e544e7f5eac59f2e345b45abf","tid":1376342,"uid":239265,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:06:22.000Z","msg":"投訴警察！"},{"pid":"39619d77b1fac3c2bd467db25b87558208129869","tid":1376342,"uid":47905,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-