%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=0eb0d2c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wGX_Vgq-1G0</a><br />\n\t<br />\n </div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">【Hongkongers! Assemble! 】<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n勿忘初衷，五大訴求！</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求<br />\n捍衛自由 不徹不散</span></strong></ins><br />\n 1. 徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n 2. 釋放所有因反送中被捕人士並承諾永不追究<br />\n 3. 撤回612暴動定性<br />\n 4. 追究警察濫權濫暴(包括721元朗官警黑勾結事件)，成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n 5. 立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1374609/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1374609/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"34a5b66610f3462352180e52443a892e59f645f1","tid":1376342,"uid":16792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2d07d606565dca21979d1590b52502b3391cf50a","tid":1376342,"uid":59922,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T10:42:07.000Z","msg":"舊嘅留低出化驗報告<br />\n新嘅拎埋啲單入小額錢債CLAIM班魔物錢得唔得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T22:00:21.000Z","msg":"應該得，咁樣其實係刑事毁壞嚟，幾百個人一次過告成功率應該會高啲"},{"pid":"0ae0267d2bef704997052f96ab4737642faa00d7","tid":1376342,"uid":16792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f49aa37a544d0d20a74300ff2bff71012747b133","tid":1376342,"uid":87735,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:17:35.000Z","msg":"落中上環派傳單或連儂牆傳遞畀街坊知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T22:00:54.000Z","msg":"要將催淚彈可以殺人呢個事實傳遞開去"},{"pid":"4f81d435fbcf56d97c0c9bef330037ca1d8dc208","tid":1376342,"uid":16792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aea21bc3a17a86d60d1e362c8e1840181bb0d256","tid":1376342,"uid":34877,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T19:01:03.000Z","msg":"小額錢債告警務署長<br />\n唔使律師自己搞都得"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T22:05:33.000Z","msg":"有得諗"},{"pid":"9d3b7e23d58e3c95743ee4bc2eed843a3a6778bf","tid":1376342,"uid":205566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r